                        "name": "'jsa",
                        "displayName": "Tomas Korcak",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Totally agree with Gunter. It is the basic functionallity. Why  would i have to create new object while i can reuse some. Please consider that. I need fx. clearRecipients(), clearSubject().",
